<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Clowdzilla</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container nav">
      <a href="#top" class="brand" aria-label="Clowdzilla home">
        <div class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true"><span></span></div>
        <span>Clowdzilla</span>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#idea">Idea</a>
        <a href="#how">How it works</a>
        <a href="#updates">Updates</a>
      </nav>
      <a class="nav-cta" href="#updates">Get updates</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <div class="eyebrow">Early-stage project</div>
          <h1>Cut through the noise. Buy with more confidence.</h1>
          <p>
            Clowdzilla is exploring a better way to make buying decisions when reviews feel unreliable, brands drift,
            and research becomes a chore. The idea is still taking shape. Join the list to follow the project as it evolves.
          </p>

          <div class="email-card" id="updates">
            <form class="email-form">
              <label class="sr-only" for="email">Email address</label>
              <input id="email" type="email" placeholder="Enter your email for updates" aria-label="Email address" />
              <button type="submit">Join the waitlist</button>
            </form>
            <p class="form-note">No spam. Just occasional updates and early previews.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="blob"></div>

          <div class="logo-card">
            <img src="clowdzilla-logo.png" alt="Clowdzilla logo" class="logo-image" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer"></footer>
</body>
</html>
